You did 2137 with Dimach, 1584 with Shen, 2994 with brawls and 1849 with punches. During that time the patroller did 655 damage.<br>
Patroller gets slaughtered in ~15 seconds, you are barely hurt, you MA skill is locked for a long time (9 minutes?) and Dimach is locked for 30 minutes.<br>
<br>
